{"tid":2029430,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"小學教師涉慢駛堵路 警長54977鍾宏業：「 X！你係唔係當我哋交通警流㗎？」","createTime":"2020-05-22T08:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T06:42:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ff944cd191712892439997a512e286f1722b5120","tid":2029430,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200522/4P7NRUUKO3UQLKR4JQFZJTNJKQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200522%2F4P7NRUUKO3UQLKR4JQFZJTNJKQ%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=6eb2ad06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200522%2F4P7NRUUKO3UQLKR4JQFZJTNJKQ%2F&h=747f4e46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200522/4P7NRUUKO3UQLKR4JQFZJTNJKQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n辯方繼續詳列眾警連環向被告施襲的過程，並揭露所謂提膝撞肚，可能是由鍾的同袍托起被告的腿時所引致。辯方道出被告版本，指警員截停時稱：「用電話喎你。身份證、車牌。」被告交出證件後開車門，卻突遭警員拉下車並推往一旁。被告稱正返工，鍾反問：「返工你又喺度兜？」被告否認後遭鍾以粗口責罵：「 X！你係唔係當我哋交通警流㗎？」另一警員亦謂：「X！和你塞吖嗱？你玩X完喇今次！」及後扯被告的頭髮。"},{"pid":"31110dc2c02f53c0a5739ec6af91d9b3ed644ca9","tid":2029430,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"5009bd9185f1d5c01fbe45f4d56f86c1fb4ad638","tid":2029430,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:32:39.000Z","msg":"誠實可靠證人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" c