:12.000Z","msg":"屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82d14ce45a419c162adda78ce58ba4d78388df8","tid":2029430,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"係人既都知你膠狗戰力最撚高 每次都實彈真槍"},{"pid":"cb170c8e2c6f0f0160058e5a859b869718e8ddcd","tid":2029430,"uid":65556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"阿鍾宏業 你做交警甴真係幾廢下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbKntKz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbKntKz.png&h=c040a635&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3e849b2fe2a3fa473ccea89f2cecd17eeab0af0","tid":2029430,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic1.xuehuaimg.com/proxy/baijia/https://f10.baidu.com/it/u=518954454,2350942195&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=639&amp;h=359&amp;s=1DE068D956E2351504A9D0080300F0D1&amp;access=215967316\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic1.xuehuaimg.com%2Fproxy%2Fbaijia%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ff10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D518954454%2C2350942195%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D639%26h%3D359%26s%3D1DE068D956E2351504A9D0080300F0D1%26access%3D215967316&h=ca22814b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"796d750ef8f958391f49da340d1988294587bee2","tid":2029430,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mikFfuL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmikFfuL.png&h=e5a0ada7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom 蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03935ed1f93e4aa61baab8ed13d7f90378d2c1e8","tid":2029430,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"點解仲可以比吳重儀判？　<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%90%B3%E9%87%8D%E5%84%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2584%2580&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=afc1bf65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%90%B3%E9%87%8D%E5%84%80</a><br />\n<br />\n爭議<br />\n大埔餐廳廚師襲環保署職員涉違犯終院案例指示<br />\n於2018年3月，一名於大埔「盧爸爸私房菜」任職的廚師被控襲擊一名環保署職員，被原審裁判官吳重儀判罪名成立。但該名廚師不服上訴至高院，代表律師張達明於法庭上批評，在處理是否誣告的案件中，終院案例指示，法庭不可揣測對方的動機。惟原審裁判官不斷質問上訴人，又批評吳作為原審裁判官，對上訴人存有偏見、邏輯有問題，很快就覺得一名公職人員不會誣捏人。[2]<br />\n<br />\n以「我知嚟做乜？」回應法庭上警暴投訴<br />\n於2020年武漢肺炎事件期間，政府徵用美孚翠雅山房作檢疫中心，引來美孚居民抗議，其中兩名被捕男子被指堵路及襲警，分別被落案控以在公眾地方擾亂秩序及襲警罪。其中一被告向法庭投訴，在警署內被人笠膠袋「由頭打到腳」，及於警署內被警告切勿投訴或找律師，「除非你以後唔再出嚟，否則一定搵到你」，但裁判官吳重儀回應：「我知道嚟做乜嘢？我又唔係監警會！」代表律師則回應，上述投訴對審訊有影響，讓法庭紀錄在案，有其重要性。[3][4]而具有法律背景的時事評論員王岸然則批評吳重儀不願去了解一件案件的多方面事故，是失職及不合格，又指年輕人若被警方濫用私刑，警員所犯的罪遠比青年在警民衝突時揮拳襲警嚴重。[5]"}]}